Package org.jvoicexml.interpreter.grammar

This package contains the classes to handle the grammars.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
GrammarIdentifier The GrammarIdentifier interface declares a couple of methods to identify a certain grammar document.
GrammarTransformer The GrammarHandler interface defines a couple of methods to process a grammar document from a source type into a target type.
 

Class Summary
GrammarProcessorHelper The GrammarProcessorHelper provides several methods to the GrammarProcessor class.
JVoiceXmlGrammarProcessor The GrammarProcessor is the main entry point for grammar processing.
JVoiceXmlGrammarRegistry Implementation of a GrammarRegistry.
RuleNameCache The RuleNameCache provides some kinf of name mapping.
 

Package org.jvoicexml.interpreter.grammar Description

This package contains the classes to handle the grammars.
